      * exist nType + cId ?
      i := ASCAN(s_aPObjList[ nWinNum+1 ], {|x| x:nType==oWPaint:nType .and. x:cId==oWPaint:cId})

   if i > 0
      * so we are about to overwrite now...
      //::Hide() is ideal, but it can be slow
